trans-unit.source: Thrown when an attempt is made to add an object to the identity cache by using a key that is already being used.
trans-unit.target: Utlöses när ett försök görs att lägga till ett objekt i cacheminnet identitet med hjälp av en nyckel som redan används.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Data.Linq.DuplicateKeyException"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Data.Linq.DuplicateKeyException"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The duplicate key that caused the exception to be thrown.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Data.Linq.DuplicateKeyException"></xref> class by referencing the duplicate key and providing an error message.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Data.Linq.DuplicateKeyException"> </xref> klassen genom att referera till dubblettnyckel och ett felmeddelande.

trans-unit.source: The duplicate key that caused the exception to be thrown.
The message to appear when the exception is thrown.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Data.Linq.DuplicateKeyException"></xref> class by referencing the duplicate key, providing an error message, and specifying the exception that caused this exception to be thrown.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Data.Linq.DuplicateKeyException"> </xref> klassen genom att referera till dubblettnyckel, tillhandahåller ett felmeddelande och ange undantag som orsakade det här undantagsfel.

trans-unit.source: The duplicate key that caused the exception to be thrown.
The message to appear when the exception is thrown.
The previous exception that caused the <xref href="System.Data.Linq.DuplicateKeyException"></xref> exception to be thrown.
trans-unit.target: Tidigare undantaget som orsakat den <xref href="System.Data.Linq.DuplicateKeyException"> </xref> undantagsfel.

trans-unit.source: Gets the object that caused the exception.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar det objekt som orsakade undantaget.

trans-unit.source: The object that caused the exception.
